g510 (0.1.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian/Ubuntu package release.
  * Supports Logitech G510 and G510s keyboards.
  * Auto-detects model via lsusb (G510 vs G510s).
  * Requires hid-lg-g15 kernel module (Linux 5.5+).
  * Two binary packages: g510-daemon and g510-gui.
  * Features: G1-G18 macros, MR record, RGB backlight, LCD GamePanel,
    media keys, volume wheel, D-Bus interface, JSON profiles.
  * G510s extras: headphone/mic mute LEDs, game-mode key.

 -- g510 contributors <fariaz@users.noreply.github.com>  Fri, 28 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
